-- StanChart extends sanctions compliance deal with U.S. authorities
-- By Simon Jessop
-- Wed Dec 10, 2014 02:15AM EST
-- None



LONDON, Dec 10 (Reuters) - Standard Chartered <STAN.L> has agreed to extend deferred prosecution agreements (DPAs) with U.S. authorities over its sanctions compliance programme, it said on Wednesday.[ID:nL1N0TT27Z]

